## Stat Pills
Centered flex layout below project descriptions. Base style for light cards, `--accent` variant for highlighted pills. Dark cards get inverted colors via `.project-card--dark .stat-pill`.

## Expandable Sections
`<details class="project-expand">` with `<summary>More about this project</summary>` pattern. Used on all four portfolio projects and the About "Agency Years" section.

## FlowForm (Contact Funnel)

6-screen multi-step lead qualification form:

1. **What's ready to move?** (single select, "I'd rather just email you" skips to contact)
2. **What are we building?** (multi select)
3. **Where are you in the process?** (single)
4. **How urgent is this?** (single)
5. **Budget comfort zone** (single)
6. **Contact info** (name, email, preferred contact, optional phone, textarea)

Confirmation screen with animated gear SVG. Submits to Netlify Forms. Integrated with gamification scoring.

## Gamification System

Point-based scoring system tracking user engagement:
- Scroll depth, hover interactions, nav clicks, gallery navigation
- FlowForm steps (50 pts each), FlowForm completion (1,000 pts)
- Score displayed in nav bar, modal explainer on click
- Stored in localStorage

## Interactive Features

| Feature | Scope | Trigger |
|---------|-------|---------|
| Scroll progress bar | Global | Scroll position |
| Blur-reveal text | Section headings | IntersectionObserver |
| Stat counters | "23+", "10" | IntersectionObserver |
| Speech bubble morph | Hero CTA | Load sequence / scroll |
| Green underline wipe | Section outro | Load sequence / scroll position |
| Cursor spotlight | Dark project cards, Partners | mousemove |
| 3D tilt | Testimonial + essential cards | mousemove |
| Magnetic buttons | Hero CTA only | mousemove (disabled past 50% scroll) |
| Gallery dot indicators | Project galleries | scroll sync |
| Rotating words | Services headline | setInterval |
| Service icon animations | Eye, blocks, rocket | scroll (500ms stagger) + hover |
| Floating shapes | Background circles/squares | mousemove + requestAnimationFrame |
| Section zoom reveal | All reveal targets | IntersectionObserver (scale 0.97→1) |
| FlowForm progression | Contact section | Click-driven step navigation |
| Gamification scoring | Global | Various interactions |

## Animation Principles

- Use `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` for reveals and morphs
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` — all JS animations check this
- Stagger grid children at 0.12s intervals
- Service card scroll animations stagger at 500ms
- Hero entrance sequence: headline letters → tagline → button → underline → bubble morph
- Keep transitions under 1s for interactions, up to 1.2s for reveals

## Project Galleries

- Horizontal scroll with `scroll-snap-type: x mandatory`
- Slides: `92vw` mobile, `min(72vw, 960px)` desktop
- Ideal image dimensions: **1920 × 1200** (16:10) for retina, minimum 1024px wide
- Center-snap with peek of adjacent slides
- Nav arrows + dot indicators + click-to-navigate on partial slides
- Team credit label centered between nav arrows via CSS Grid
- Placeholder slides use gradient backgrounds or inline styles
- Dark cards get inverted placeholder/dot/arrow colors
- Vimeo embeds use `loading="lazy"` and `object-fit: cover`

## Performance

- **Lazy loading**: All images and iframes below the fold use `loading="lazy"`
- **Hero preload**: `<link rel="preload">` for the hero image (LCP element)
- **Hero image**: Compressed to 136KB (from 1.1MB original)
- **Font display**: `display=swap` on Google Fonts to prevent FOIT
- **Initial load**: ~280KB (down from ~5.5MB)
- **Single-file architecture**: All CSS/JS inline in `index.html`, no external scripts

## SEO & AI Indexability

- **robots.txt**: Welcomes all search engines + AI crawlers (GPTBot, ClaudeBot, PerplexityBot, Google-Extended, Cohere)
- **sitemap.xml**: Homepage + /uses page
- **llms.txt**: Plain-text site summary for AI model ingestion
- **Canonical URL**: `<link rel="canonical" href="https://bpwcislo.com/">`
- **JSON-LD structured data**: Person, ProfessionalService, WebSite, 4 CreativeWork entries, 4 Review entries
- **Open Graph + Twitter Card**: 1200×630 landscape OG image (`og-share.jpg`)
- **Semantic HTML**: `<main>`, `<nav>`, `<section>`, `<footer>`, aria-labels throughout

## File Structure

```
bpwcislo.com/
